fields.description:
When running a Titanium app on Sim / device, the following error log is shown on startup and should be handled:
{code}
[ERROR] zygote64: The String#value field is not present on Android versions >= 6.0
{code}

In general: There are many noisy zygote / APSAnalytics logs (testing on SDK 7.2.0), do we have this fixed for later versions already?
